message.text:
🔥𝘾𝘼𝙇𝙇𝙄𝙉𝙂 𝘼𝙇𝙇 𝙋𝙊𝙒𝙀𝙍𝙇𝙄𝙁𝙏𝘼𝙈𝙎! 🔥

The FEU Powerlifting Team is finally here — and YOU🫵 have the chance to be part of history as we form the first-ever official powerlifting team across all FEU branches! 🔰

Whether you’re a seasoned lifter or just starting your strength journey 🏋️, this is your opportunity to represent FEU🔰, build your strength, and carry the Tamaraw pride on and off the platform. 🐃💪🏻

We are also working towards becoming an accredited student group, and your participation is an important step in making this possible. For now, we’re gathering responses for census purposes and to connect with all students who may be interested.

If powerlifting speaks to your strength 💪🏻, we humbly ask you to take a moment to answer our form 🙇🏻‍♂️ . Your response can help shape the future of FEU’s lifting community.
Let’s lift FEU together! 💪🏻🐃🔰🔥

#FEUPowerlifting #OneStrongMalakas #TamarawStrong #BeBrave

The FEU Powerlifting Team is finally here — and YOU🫵 have the chance to be part of history as we form the first-ever official powerlifting team across all FEU branches! 🔰

Whether you’re a seasoned lifter or just starting your strength journey 🏋️, this is your opportunity to represent FEU🔰, build your strength, and carry the Tamaraw pride on and off the platform. 🐃💪🏻

We are also working towards becoming an accredited student group, and your participation is an important step in making this possible. For now, we’re gathering responses for census purposes and to connect with all students who may be interested.

If powerlifting speaks to your strength 💪🏻, we humbly ask you to take a moment to answer our form 🙇🏻‍♂️ . Your response can help shape the future of FEU’s lifting community.
Let’s lift FEU together! 💪🏻🐃🔰🔥

#FEUPowerlifting #OneStrongMalakas #TamarawStrong #BeBrave
